AddAddressBook.title: AddAddressBook
AddAddressBook.summary: Creates an address book for access control. Supported address book types are IP address books, Elastic Compute Service (ECS) tag-based address books, port address books, and domain address books. An ECS tag-based address book includes the public IP addresses of the ECS instances that have specific tags.
